| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4868 — Recovery Inhibition (dAn0n)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 03bb41ae-2037-5773-9a1a-e356582c46c2"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
